text: Crow Hollow is a 1952 British mystery movie directed by Michael McCarthy and is based on the 1950 novel Crow Hollow by Dorothy Eden. It stars Donald Houston, Natasha Parry, Patricia Owens, Esma Cannon and Nora Nicholson. == Other websites == * Category:1952 movies Category:1950s mystery movies Category:British mystery movies Category:Movies based on books Category:Movies directed by Michael McCarthy
